headline: How Hulk Hogan shaped TKO and the pro wrestling business
summary: Professional wrestler legend Hulk Hogan died at 71 on Thursday, July 24. Yahoo Finance Executive Editor Brian Sozzi examines Hogan's legacy, including how he contributed to making pro wrestling mainstream and his impact on UFC parent company TKO (TKO). CFRA Research chief investment strategist Sam Stovall offers additional insight into TKO and the state of the live sports streaming space alongside Yahoo Finance Senior Reporters Ines Ferré and Brooke DiPalma. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Opening Bid here.
